 with\na model combining X-ray irradiation with the disc instability, but with the\nadded ingredient of a very large disc in this long period system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Mar 1998 18:15:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-30"}
