quilibrium grows with $N$, at least near the critical point. Our results\nconstitute an interesting bridge between Hamiltonian chaos in many degrees of\nfreedom systems and equilibrium thermodynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 1998 10:31:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 May 1998 08:48:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-13"}
